s\",\n      \"Manual back-office contract processing and validation\",\n      \"Fragmented product and policy specifications\"\n    ],\n    agents: [\n      { name: \"Banking Knowledge Agent\", role: \"Instant semantic retrieval across internal policy archives\" },\n      { name: \"Relationship Manager Copilot\", role: \"Hedge-fund-grade client dossier drafting and advisory support\" },\n      { name: \"Contract Intelligence Agent\", role: \"Automated analysis of corporate loan and credit agreements\" }\n    ],\n    color: \"#009DFF\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"insurance\",\n    title: \"Insurance\",\n    path: \"/industries/insurance\",\n    category: \"PROPERTY, CASUALTY & LIFE\",\n    desc: \"Accelerate claim lifecycle velocity and automate policy parsing using secure multi-agent pipelines configured with custom risk scoring.\",\n    challenges: [\n      \"High claims processing operational overhead\",\n      \"Manual assessment of multi-source inspection reports and photos\",\n      \"Inconsistent policy terms analysis and validation\",\n      \"Long queue times for client response and settlement\"\n    ],\n    agents: [\n      { name: \"Claims Triage Agent\", role: \"Automated parsing and categorization of inbound damage files\" },\n      { name: \"Policy Intelligence Agent\", role: \"Instant comparison of incoming claims against coverage limits\" },\n      { name: \"Underwriting Copilot\", role: \"Structured risk profiling and data compilation for underwriters\" }\n    ],\n    color: \"#FFFFFF\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"manufacturing\",\n    title: \"Advanced Manufacturing\",\n    category: \"FACTORY FLOOR & LOGISTICS\",\n    desc: \"Calibrate real-time IoT anomaly detection, automated inventory forecasting, and computer-vision sorting streams to maximize line yield.\",\n    challenges: [\n      \"Unplanned machine downtime costing millions per hour\",\n      \"Mismatched materials ordering with active assembly runs\",\n      \"Manual and error-prone surface quality inspections\"\n    ],\n    agents: [\n      { name: \"Predictive Maintenance Hub\", role: \"Live IoT telemetry and vibration analysis coordinator\" },\n      { name: \"Supply Demand Coordinator\", role: \"Automated ERP balancing and logistics synchronization\" },\n      { name: \"Quality Defect Vision\", role: \"Defect taxonomy cataloging via edge camera feeds\" }\n    ],\n    color: \"#E4000F\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"logistics\",\n    title: \"Supply Chain & Logistics\",\n    category: \"GLOBAL TRANSIT & STORAGE\",\n    desc: \"Coordinate autonomous routing algorithms, real-time slotting policies, and semantic bill of lading parsers for high-velocity distribution.\",\n    challenges: [\n      \"Weather, port, and labor transit volatility patterns\",\n      \"Inefficient storage layouts and static inventory slotting\",\n      \"Manual customs, manifest, and freight document entry\"\n    ],\n    agents: [\n      { name: \"Autonomous Routing Coordinator\", role: \"Dynamic multi-modal route adjustment\" },\n      { name: \"Warehouse Inventory Planner\", role: \"Automated warehouse optimization based on product velocity\" },\n      { name: \"Customs Clearance Parser\", role: \"Semantic extraction of bills of lading and invoices\" }\n    ],\n    color: \"#009DFF\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"healthcare\",\n    title: \"Healthcare & Life Sciences\",\n    category: \"CLINICAL RESEARCH & PATIENT OPS\",\n    desc: \"Implement privacy-compliant medical record parsing pipelines and clinical trials logistics agents operating under strict access guardrails.\",\n    challenges: [\n      \"High manual burden of medical records parsing\",\n      \"Complex compliance validation during clinical trial recruitment\",\n      \"Fragmented search across bio-pharmaceutical papers\"\n    ],\n    agents: [\n      { name: \"Medical Record Parser\", role: \"De-identified diagnostic extraction under strict security\" },\n      { name: \"Trials Coordinator Agent\", role: \"Patient-to-criteria matching and safety monitoring\" },\n      { name: \"HIPAA Guardrail Agent\", role: \"Real-time sanitization of outbound conversational outputs\" }\n    ],\n    color: \"#FFFFFF\"\n  }\n];\n\nconst CROSS_INDUSTRY_CHALLENGES = [\n  {\n    title: \"Legacy Core Decoupling\",\n    desc: \"Most enterprise sectors run on 30-year-old mainframe systems. GFF AI decouples cognitive reasoning from direct database writes through secure read-only mirrors and immutable action queues.\",\n    icon: (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#E4000F]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10\" />\n      </svg>\n    )\n  },\n  {\n    title: \"Continuous Compliance Auditing\",\n    desc: \"Regulations are not static. Our architecture embeds sovereign compliance policies directly into the LLM orchestration logic as active system guardrails, recording complete execution trails for auditability.\",\n    icon: (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#009DFF]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z\" />\n      </svg>\n    )\n  },\n  {\n    title: \"Multi-Modal Information Isolation\",\n    desc: \"Enterprise data is highly unstructured—spread across scans, spreadsheets, emails, and call transcripts. GFF AI builds private, local semantic databases with high-accuracy OCR pre-processing.\",\n    icon: (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M8 7v8a2 2 0 002 2h6M8 7V5a2 2 0 012-2h4.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l4.414 4.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V15a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2M8 7H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2v-2\" />\n      </svg>\n    )\n  },\n  {\n    title: \"Human-in-the-Loop Safeguards\",\n    desc: \"Autonomous action requires oversight. All transaction dispatches, payment routing, and policy changes are queued in our human review panel before execution, preventing unilateral mistakes.\",\n    icon: (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#E4000F]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z\" />\n      </svg>\n    )\n  }\n];\n\nexport default function IndustriesPage() {\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState(\"financial-services\");\n  const selectedIndustry = INDUSTRIES_DATA.find((ind) => ind.id === activeTab) || INDUSTRIES_DATA[0];\n\n  const [activeArchLayer, setActiveArchLayer] = useState(\"cognitive\");\n\n  const archLayers = {\n    ingest: {\n      title: \"Data Extraction & Gateway\",\n      desc: \"Connects to core legacy banking systems, CRM databases, claims queues, and documents.\",\n      tech: \"Kafka / gRPC / OCR Pipeline\"\n    },\n    cognitive: {\n      title: \"Sovereign Cognitive Router\",\n      desc: \"Assesses intent, splits queries into parallel tool requests, and enforces regional safety policies.\",\n      tech: \"GFF AI Custom LLM Engine\"\n    },\n    action: {\n      title: \"Secure Dispatched Outbound\",\n      desc: \"Triggers API payloads, schedules database updates, and queues actions for human approvals.\",\n      tech: \"Temporal / Webhook Gateway\"\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      {/* 1. Hero Section */}\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Enterprise Vertical Architectures\"\n        title=\"AI Engineered for Your Industry\"\n        highlightedWord=\"Industry\"\n        description=\"GFF AI engineers custom cognitive frameworks calibrated for the strict security, compliance, and velocity needs of enterprise sectors.\"\n      />\n\n      {/* 2. Interactive Industry Selector & Details Section */}\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-20\">\n        <div className=\"text-center max-w-[800px] mx-auto mb-12\">\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#009DFF] font-semibold\">INTERACTIVE MAP</span>\n          <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[36px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n            Industry Cognitive Blueprints\n          </h2>\n          <p className=\"mt-3 text-[14px] leading-[1.6] text-white/60 font-light\">\n            Select an industry below to inspect core operational bottlenecks, deployed cognitive agents, and custom technical blueprints.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Tab Buttons */}\n        <div className=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 md:gap-3 mb-8 max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\">\n          {INDUSTRIES_DATA.map((ind) => (\n            <button\n              key={ind.id}\n              onClick={() => setActiveTab(ind.id)}\n              className={`px-4 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[12.5px] font-semibold transition-all duration-300 border ${\n                activeTab === ind.id\n                  ? \"bg-white text-black border-white shadow-lg\"\n                  : \"bg-white/5 text-white/70 border-white/5 hover:text-white hover:border-white/12\"\n              }`}\n            >\n              {ind.title}\n            </button>\n          ))}\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Interactive Industry Details Showcase Card */}\n        <div className=\"rounded-[28px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/80 backdrop-blur-[16px] p-6 lg:p-10 max-w-[1300px] mx-auto relative overflow-hidden group\">\n          <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[30%] h-[30%] bg-gradient-to-bl from-white/[0.02] to-transparent pointer-events-none\" />\n          \n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-start relative z-10\">\n            {/* Left Column: Summary and Link */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-between h-full min-h-[300px]\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono tracking-[0.18em] text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">\n                  {selectedIndustry.category}\n                </span>\n                <h3 className=\"text-[26px] sm:text-[32px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n                  {selectedIndustry.title}\n                </h3>\n                <p className=\"mt-4 text-[14px] leading-[1.6] text-white/60 font-light\">\n                  {selectedIndustry.desc}\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"mt-8\">\n                {selectedIndustry.path ? (\n                  <a\n                    href={selectedIndustry.path}\n                    className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-[13px] font-semibold text-white transition-all bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/15\"\n                  >\n                    <span>Explore Strategy & Agents</span>\n                    <svg className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                      <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\" />\n                    </svg>\n                  </a>\n                ) : (\n                  <div className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5\">\n                    <span>Tailored Blueprint Design Active</span>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Middle Column: Challenges */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-4 border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-white/5 pt-6 lg:pt-0 lg:pl-8\">\n              <h4 className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 font-bold\">\n                CORE VERTICAL CHALLENGES\n              </h4>\n              <ul className=\"space-y-4\">\n                {selectedIndustry.challenges.map((challenge, idx) => (\n                  <li key={idx} className=\"flex gap-3\">\n                    <span className=\"shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[11px] text-[#E4000F] font-mono font-bold\">\n                      {idx + 1}\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[13px] text-white/70 font-light leading-[1.4]\">\n                      {challenge}\n                    </span>\n                  </li>\n                ))}\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Right Column: AI Agents Blueprint */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-3 border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-white/5 pt-6 lg:pt-0 lg:pl-8\">\n              <h4 className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 font-bold\">\n                ACTIVE COGNITIVE BLUEPRINTS\n              </h4>\n              <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                {selectedIndustry.agents.map((agent, idx) => (\n                  <div key={idx} className=\"p-3.5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider block\">\n                      {agent.name}\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[12px] text-white/60 font-light mt-1 block leading-normal\">\n                      {agent.role}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 3. Common Cross-Industry Challenge Patterns */}\n      <div className=\"bg-[#030304]/40 border-t border-b border-white/5 py-24\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16\">\n          <div className=\"max-w-[800px] mb-16\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">SYSTEMATIC FRICTION</span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[38px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n              Common Challenge Patterns\n            </h2>\n            <p className=\"mt-3 text-[14px] leading-[1.6] text-white/60 font-light\">\n              Every enterprise sector faces shared underlying issues when integrating production-grade cognitive systems. GFF AI solves these patterns at the foundational layer.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8\">\n            {CROSS_INDUSTRY_CHALLENGES.map((challenge, idx) => (\n              <div key={idx} className=\"p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050506]/80 flex gap-5 hover:border-white/10 transition-all\">\n                <div className=\"shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center border border-white/5\">\n                  {challenge.icon}\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <h3 className=\"text-[16px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight\">\n                    {challenge.title}\n                  </h3>\n                  <p className=\"mt-2 text-[13px] leading-[1.6] text-white/60 font-light\">\n                    {challenge.desc}\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 4. Interactive Reference Solution Architecture */}\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 py-24\">\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center\">\n          {/* Left Text */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-5\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">BLUEPRINT OVERVIEW</span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[38px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n              Cross-Industry Cognitive Reference Architecture\n            </h2>\n            <p className=\"mt-4 text-[14.5px] leading-[1.6] text-white/70 font-light\">\n              We separate system functions into clean, isolated security tiers. Click the technical layers in the diagram to inspect specifications for regulatory-compliant flow isolation.\n            </p>\n\n            <div className=\"mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3\">\n              {Object.entries(archLayers).map(([key, layer]) => (\n                <button\n                  key={key}\n                  onClick={() => setActiveArchLayer(key)}\n                  className={`p-4 rounded-xl text-left border transition-all ${\n                    activeArchLayer === key\n                      ? \"bg-white/5 border-white/15 text-white\"\n                      : \"bg-transparent border-transparent text-white/50 hover:text-white/80\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider block font-semibold mb-0.5\">\n                    {key === \"ingest\" ? \"LAYER 01\" : key === \"cognitive\" ? \"LAYER 02\" : \"LAYER 03\"}\n                  </span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[14px] font-bold tracking-tight\">{layer.title}</span>\n                </button>\n              ))}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Right Visual interactive map */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 rounded-[28px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050506]/60 backdrop-blur-[12px] p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center mb-6\">\n              <svg className=\"w-full max-w-[500px] h-[280px]\" viewBox=\"0 0 500 280\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                {/* Connector Pipes */}\n                <path d=\"M250 40 L250 110 M250 150 L250 210\" stroke=\"url(#lineGrad)\" strokeWidth=\"2\" strokeDasharray=\"5 5\" />\n                \n                {/* Tier 1 Ingestion */}\n                <g onClick={() => setActiveArchLayer(\"ingest\")} className=\"cursor-pointer group\">\n                  <rect\n                    x=\"80\" y=\"20\" width=\"340\" height=\"40\" rx=\"10\"\n                    fill={activeArchLayer === \"ingest\" ? \"#E4000F\" : \"#0A0A0C\"}\n                    stroke={activeArchLayer === \"ingest\" ? \"white\" : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"}\n                    strokeWidth=\"1.5\" className=\"transition-all duration-300\"\n                  />\n                  <text x=\"250\" y=\"44\" fill=\"white\" fontSize=\"11\" fontWeight=\"600\" textAnchor=\"middle\" className=\"uppercase tracking-[0.08em] font-mono\">\n                    01. DATA INGESTION GATEWAYS\n                  </text>\n                </g>\n\n                {/* Tier 2 Orchestration */}\n                <g onClick={() => setActiveArchLayer(\"cognitive\")} className=\"cursor-pointer group\">\n                  <rect\n                    x=\"60\" y=\"110\" width=\"380\" height=\"50\" rx=\"12\"\n                    fill={activeArchLayer === \"cognitive\" ? \"url(#brandGrad)\" : \"#0A0A0C\"}\n                    stroke={activeArchLayer === \"cognitive\" ? \"white\" : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"}\n                    strokeWidth=\"1.5\" className=\"transition-all duration-300\"\n                  />\n                  <text x=\"250\" y=\"139\" fill=\"white\" fontSize=\"12\" fontWeight=\"700\" textAnchor=\"middle\" className=\"uppercase tracking-[0.08em] font-mono\">\n                    02. GFF AI COGNITIVE CORE\n                  </text>\n                </g>\n\n                {/* Tier 3 Outbound */}\n                <g onClick={() => setActiveArchLayer(\"action\")} className=\"cursor-pointer group\">\n                  <rect\n                    x=\"80\" y=\"210\" width=\"340\" height=\"40\" rx=\"10\"\n                    fill={activeArchLayer === \"action\" ? \"#009DFF\" : \"#0A0A0C\"}\n                    stroke={activeArchLayer === \"action\" ? \"white\" : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"}\n                    strokeWidth=\"1.5\" className=\"transition-all duration-300\"\n                  />\n                  <text x=\"250\" y=\"234\" fill=\"white\" fontSize=\"11\" fontWeight=\"600\" textAnchor=\"middle\" className=\"uppercase tracking-[0.08em] font-mono\">\n                    03. ACTION DISPATCH & REVIEWS\n                  </text>\n                </g>\n\n                <defs>\n                  <linearGradient id=\"brandGrad\" x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"380\" y2=\"0\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\">\n                    <stop stopColor=\"#E4000F\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"1\" stopColor=\"#009DFF\" />\n                  </linearGradient>\n                  <linearGradient id=\"lineGrad\" x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"0\" y2=\"280\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\">\n                    <stop stopColor=\"#E4000F\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"0.5\" stopColor=\"#FFFFFF\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"1\" stopColor=\"#009DFF\" />\n                  </linearGradient>\n                </defs>\n              </svg>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-6\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">\n                Layer Specification\n              </span>\n              <h4 className=\"text-[16px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight mt-1\">\n                {archLayers[activeArchLayer as keyof typeof archLayers].title}\n              </h4>\n              <p className=\"mt-2 text-[13px] leading-[1.5] text-white/60 font-light\">\n                {archLayers[activeArchLayer as keyof typeof archLayers].desc}\n              </p>\n              <div className=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">ENGINEERED INTEGRATION</span>\n                <span className=\"px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-[4px] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/80\">\n                  {archLayers[activeArchLayer as keyof typeof archLayers].tech}\n                </span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 5. CTA to Build AI for Your Industry */}\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24\">\n        <PremiumCTA\n          title=\"Build Autonomous Cognitive Architecture for Your Industry\"\n          description=\"Consult GFF AI's system engineers to spec out your custom compliance workflows, private document ingestion mirrors, and human-in-the-loop review queues.\"\n          primaryLabel=\"Consult Systems Architects\"\n          primaryHref=\"/contact\"\n          secondaryLabel=\"Platform Specs\"\n          secondaryHref=\"/platforms\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
